        <num>CC 2482</num>
        <heading>2482.  Things not in possession of seller</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2482.  Things not in possession of seller
When at the time of the sale the seller is not in possession of the thing sold he must obtain possession at his cost and deliver the thing to the buyer.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=109527</p>
